<h1 class='article_title buffer'>
World’s Top Serial Bird Killers Put Infamous Windmills to Shame
</h1>

<div class='entry_wrap'>
<div class='byline'>
<span class='author' itemprop='author'>By Tom Randall</span>
<span class='divider'></span>
<span bgdatestamp='mmm d, yyyy h:MM TT Z' bglocalize='true' class='date' epoch='1398098369000'>
2014-04-21T16:39:29Z
</span>
<span class='divider divider_second'></span>
<div class='byline_links'>
<![if (!IE)|(gte IE 8)]>
<span class='comments'>
<span class='comments_container'>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="17a05780ab990131d041005056b05fc6" href="http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-04-21/beware-the-blades-of-death-world-s-top-serial-bird-killers-.html#disqus_thread" title="Navigate to comments on this article">- Comments</a>
</span>
</span>
<![endif]>

