<a class='icon-twitter twitter_share_button' href='https://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fbloom.bg%2F1nkcFeh&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2F2014-04-21%2Fbeware-the-blades-of-death-world-s-top-serial-bird-killers-.html&amp;text=World%E2%80%99s+Top+Serial+Bird+Killers+Put+Infamous+Windmills+to+Shame&amp;via=BloombergNews' onclick="window.open(this.href, '', 'width=626,height=436');&#x000A;          return false;" rel='nofollow' target='_blank' title='Tweet this'>
